---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About Domain Echo - Our Mission to Make the Web More Social"
  description="Learn about Domain Echo's mission to create anonymous, real-time chat rooms for every website. Discover how we're making the web more social while protecting your privacy."
  keywords="about domain echo, website chat mission, anonymous browsing, privacy-first chat, social web"
  canonicalUrl="/about"
>
  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-950 to-slate-900">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-purple-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        About Domain Echo
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-400 mb-12">
        Making the web more social, one domain at a time.
      </p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Domain Echo was created with a simple idea: what if every website had its own chat room? What if you could instantly connect with others who are reading the same article, watching the same video, or browsing the same product?
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We believe the internet should be more social, more connected, and more human. Domain Echo brings people together around shared interests and experiences, all while respecting your privacy and anonymity.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">How It Started</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Domain Echo began as a weekend project to explore real-time communication on the web. We wanted to create something that was:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Anonymous</strong> - No accounts, no tracking, just conversation</li>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Instant</strong> - Real-time messaging with WebSocket technology</li>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Universal</strong> - Works on every website you visit</li>
            <li>‚úÖ <strong>Simple</strong> - One click to join, one click to chat</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">Privacy First</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                We don't collect personal data. We don't track you. We don't sell your information. Your conversations are ephemeral and anonymous.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">Open & Transparent</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                We believe in building in the open. Our code is available for review, and we're transparent about how Domain Echo works.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">Community Driven</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Domain Echo is built for the community, by the community. We listen to feedback and continuously improve based on what users want.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-indigo-400 mb-2">Free Forever</h3>
              <p class="text-slate-300">
                Domain Echo will always be free. No premium tiers, no paywalls, no ads. Just pure, simple communication.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800 mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Technology</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Domain Echo is built with modern web technologies:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-slate-300 mt-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Chrome Extension</strong> - Manifest V3 for security and performance</li>
            <li><strong>Convex</strong> - Real-time backend with WebSocket support</li>
            <li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - Type-safe code for reliability</li>
            <li><strong>Modern UI</strong> - Clean, responsive design</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-900 p-8 rounded-xl border border-slate-800">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Join the Conversation</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Ready to make the web more social? Install Domain Echo and start chatting with people who share your interests.
          </p>
          <a href="/#install" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition">
            <span class="text-xl">üåê</span>
            Get Domain Echo Free
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

